{
  "video_id": "uU1dLWm8c7o",
  "title": "The Mysterious Sand Designs On California's Beaches",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 4396.0,
      "end_time": 7020.0,
      "text": "BRANDON ANDERTON: Some would see\nit as an exercise in futility."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 7020.0,
      "end_time": 9350.0,
      "text": "It's invariably\ngoing to wash away."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 9350.0,
      "end_time": 11370.0,
      "text": "But if it gets people\nto stop and think,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 11370.0,
      "end_time": 13250.0,
      "text": "my time is well spent\nright then and there."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 13250.0,
      "end_time": 15810.0,
      "text": "LAURA LING: You were a\nprofessional motorcycle road"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 15810.0,
      "end_time": 16510.0,
      "text": "racer."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 16510.0,
      "end_time": 18690.0,
      "text": "What did you love about\nmotorcycle racing?"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 18690.0,
      "end_time": 21023.0,
      "text": "BRANDON ANDERTON: I've always\nbeen an adrenaline junkie."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 21023.0,
      "end_time": 24452.0,
      "text": "So it's just the most\nextreme circumstances"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 24452.0,
      "end_time": 25970.0,
      "text": "that you can think of."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 25970.0,
      "end_time": 28520.0,
      "text": "Being out in the elements,\nbeing on a motorcycle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 28520.0,
      "end_time": 30990.0,
      "text": "and then being able to\ncarry the speed that you"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 30990.0,
      "end_time": 32719.0,
      "text": "can through corners\nand stuff, it's"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 32719.0,
      "end_time": 36200.0,
      "text": "a perspective, an experience\nyou can't really synthesize"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 36200.0,
      "end_time": 38550.0,
      "text": "through any other means."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 38550.0,
      "end_time": 41480.0,
      "text": "LAURA LING: Have you experienced\nmany crashes and injuries?"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 41480.0,
      "end_time": 42420.0,
      "text": "LAURA LING: Oh yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 42420.0,
      "end_time": 46580.0,
      "text": "Yeah, I've broken my\nlegs three times a piece,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 46580.0,
      "end_time": 51490.0,
      "text": "my arms twice, ribs,\nprobably about six ribs."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 51490.0,
      "end_time": 54650.0,
      "text": "Disintegrated my tib,\nfib, and my femur."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 54650.0,
      "end_time": 56890.0,
      "text": "Broke my pelvis in half,\nand my lower two ribs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 56890.0,
      "end_time": 58325.0,
      "text": "and my scapula on my left side."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 58325.0,
      "end_time": 60700.0,
      "text": "LAURA LING: Racing was your\npassion, and all of a sudden,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 60700.0,
      "end_time": 62390.0,
      "text": "you weren't able\nto do that anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 62390.0,
      "end_time": 64239.0,
      "text": "How did you deal with\nthat emotionally?"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 64239.00000000001,
      "end_time": 65660.0,
      "text": "BRANDON ANDERTON:\nI was relegated"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 65660.0,
      "end_time": 68050.0,
      "text": "to living in a wheelchair\nfor about a year and a half"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 68050.0,
      "end_time": 71430.0,
      "text": "inside my condo,\nessentially a shut in."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 71430.0,
      "end_time": 74750.0,
      "text": "So I had a lot of time to\nwork out and practice moving"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 74750.0,
      "end_time": 77170.0,
      "text": "and regain my ability to walk."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 79854.0,
      "end_time": 82020.0,
      "text": "LAURA LING: Can you talk\nto me about the ritual that"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 82020.0,
      "end_time": 83380.0,
      "text": "has helped you through this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 83380.0,
      "end_time": 84338.0,
      "text": "BRANDON ANDERTON: Yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 84338.0,
      "end_time": 85040.0,
      "text": "I found art."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 85040.0,
      "end_time": 87980.0,
      "text": "And it's not something\nI grew up with doing."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 87980.0,
      "end_time": 89665.0,
      "text": "And I got the idea\none of the times"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 89665.0,
      "end_time": 91040.0,
      "text": "that I was out\nthere on the beach"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 91040.0,
      "end_time": 93990.0,
      "text": "to just start scrawling\nstuff in the sand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 93990.0,
      "end_time": 96650.0,
      "text": "and I wouldn't have to worry\nabout anybody else's judgment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 96650.0,
      "end_time": 98649.0,
      "text": "because I was there by\nmyself and the waves were"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 98649.0,
      "end_time": 100260.0,
      "text": "going to take it anyway."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 100260.0,
      "end_time": 103000.0,
      "text": "So the process for\nme is, basically,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 103000.0,
      "end_time": 105310.0,
      "text": "being with a thought,\nan emotion, or a story."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 105310.0,
      "end_time": 107638.0,
      "text": "Usually on the drive over,\nsomething will come to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 107638.0,
      "end_time": 109346.0,
      "text": "And then a shape will\nmanifest from that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 109346.0,
      "end_time": 110555.0,
      "text": "and it all starts from there."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 110555.0,
      "end_time": 112845.0,
      "text": "LAURA LING: Can you tell me\nwhat goes through your mind"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 112845.0,
      "end_time": 114410.0,
      "text": "when you're creating this art?"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 114410.0,
      "end_time": 116920.0,
      "text": "BRANDON ANDERTON: Sometimes\nthere's-- I'll have a bit"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 116920.0,
      "end_time": 117810.0,
      "text": "of a pity party."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 117810.0,
      "end_time": 118690.0,
      "text": "You know, why me?"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 118690.0,
      "end_time": 120720.0,
      "text": "You know, why has\nthis happened to me?"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 120720.0,
      "end_time": 122630.0,
      "text": "Other times, I just\nthink about what"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 122630.0,
      "end_time": 125690.0,
      "text": "life is, what consciousness\nis, why we're all here."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 125690.0,
      "end_time": 127503.0,
      "text": "LAURA LING: It sounds\nvery therapeutic."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 127503.0,
      "end_time": 128669.0,
      "text": "BRANDON ANDERTON: Extremely."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 128669.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131280.0,
      "text": "It's fundamentally changed\nwho I am as a person."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 131280.0,
      "end_time": 135060.0,
      "text": "I was in a really bad place, but\njust the creation of the art,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 135060.0,
      "end_time": 139570.0,
      "text": "in and of itself, and that\nfeeling of gratification"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 139570.0,
      "end_time": 141550.0,
      "text": "and thankfulness\nand satisfaction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 141550.0,
      "end_time": 145470.0,
      "text": "is something that\nI haven't obtained"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 145470.0,
      "end_time": 147496.0,
      "text": "from anything else in my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 149637.0,
      "end_time": 152220.0,
      "text": "LAURA LING: Do you wait for the\ntide to take the artwork away?"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 152220.0,
      "end_time": 153595.0,
      "text": "BRANDON ANDERTON:\nSometimes I do."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 153595.0,
      "end_time": 156480.0,
      "text": "It's just an affirmation of\nno matter what we do here"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 156480.0,
      "end_time": 158070.0,
      "text": "on this world,\nnature's still going"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 158070.0,
      "end_time": 160456.0,
      "text": "to come back and\nreclaim everything."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 160456.0,
      "end_time": 162810.0,
      "text": "It's a total catharsis\nfor me in that regard."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 162810.0,
      "end_time": 165285.0,
      "text": "[MUSIC PLAYING]"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 182610.0,
      "end_time": 185080.0,
      "text": "LAURA LING: And you can also\nwatch this episode of Rituals."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 185080.0,
      "end_time": 186705.0,
      "text": "MIKE SHINODA: And\nthere are other times"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 186705.0,
      "end_time": 189790.0,
      "text": "when I'm hyper-agitated."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 189790.0,
      "end_time": 195550.0,
      "text": "In my head, it's like a cyclone\nof noise, and it's loud."
    }
  ]
}